Interface IRenderSubPage

public interface IRenderSubPage

A class implements IRenderSubPage to indicate that it can render a sub-page of a page object.

public void setSubPageNumber(int subPageNumber)
Specify the sub-page number that needs to be rendered by the page view. The default sub-page number for an IPageView object is 1. It loads the first page of a multi-page report.
